{"tid":596372,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Switch 5.0版本更新後 使用第三方底座會變磚","createTime":"2018-03-17T14:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T16:10:44.000Z","uid":14065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"360819708910f462b5d823a8c761985f3da900a3","tid":596372,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:30:32.000Z","msg":"在過去一周任天堂Switch正式推送5.0.0更新。雖然新版本增加了一些功能並實施了一些改進，但不幸的是，它似乎給第三方底座帶來了重大問題。<br />\n過去一年中有不少非任天堂製造的第三方底座上市，包括Nyko這一品牌。而近日有不少任天堂Switch玩家報告說，在使用該公司的設備和最新的Switch更新之後，他的系統已經完全變磚了。<br />\n目前受損的Switch主機無法開機，同時似乎所有保存的存檔都將因此而丟失。<br />\n這絕對不是孤立的事件。 Nyko在Twitter上收到了不少投訴，許多人提出更換受損的主機，並要求賠償維修費用。<br />\nNyko方面表示，將會更換受損Switch和底座，同時請求玩家與客服團隊聯繫。<br />\n根據目前狀況，第三方底座還是暫時不要使用為好<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.sina.com.tw/article/20180317/26163296.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20180317%2F26163296.html&d=Yauu6nwW8lo3geADvX2Jgk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=6e2943f4\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.sina.com.tw/article/20180317/26163296.html</a>"},{"pid":"81cb3ed86891e61dc7ea30cd8b7f6b0e49eda0bc","tid":596372,"uid":21754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:10:00.000Z","msg":"手掣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d7efd512686d275582d313695f261c13462beb","tid":596372,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:10:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}